- x: number of bags of regular brand dog food
- y: number of bags of premium brand dog food

Definitions:
- x, y >= 0 (non-negative integers)

Objective Function:
- Minimize Cost = 20x + 35y

Constraints:
- 4x + 12y \geq 15 (calcium constraint)
- 7x + 10y \geq 20 (vitamin mix constraint)
- 10x + 16y \geq 20 (protein constraint)
